# UI Design System and Key Screen Mockups

## Design System

### Colors

#### Primary Palette
- **Primary Blue**: #1a365d - Main brand color, headers, primary buttons
- **Secondary Teal**: #2bb0ed - Accents, secondary elements, progress indicators
- **Accent Coral**: #f56565 - Call-to-action, important highlights, notifications

#### Neutral Palette
- **Dark Gray**: #2d3748 - Main text color
- **Medium Gray**: #718096 - Secondary text, icons
- **Light Gray**: #e2e8f0 - Borders, dividers
- **Lighter Gray**: #f7fafc - Backgrounds, cards
- **White**: #ffffff - Primary background

#### Functional Colors
- **Success Green**: #48bb78 - Success states, confirmations
- **Warning Amber**: #ed8936 - Warnings, cautions
- **Error Red**: #e53e3e - Errors, destructive actions
- **Info Blue**: #4299e1 - Information, help

### Typography

#### Font Families
- **Primary Font**: Inter - Clean, modern sans-serif for most UI elements
- **Heading Font**: Montserrat - For headlines and important labels
- **Monospace**: JetBrains Mono - For code samples or technical content

#### Type Scale
- **Display**: 48px / 3rem - Hero headlines
- **H1**: 36px / 2.25rem - Page titles
- **H2**: 30px / 1.875rem - Section headers
- **H3**: 24px / 1.5rem - Card headers, major elements
- **H4**: 20px / 1.25rem - Subsection headers
- **Body**: 16px / 1rem - Default body text
- **Small**: 14px / 0.875rem - Secondary information
- **XSmall**: 12px / 0.75rem - Labels, captions

### Components

#### Buttons
- **Primary Button**: Blue background, white text, rounded corners (8px)
- **Secondary Button**: White background, blue border, blue text
- **Tertiary Button**: No background/border, blue text
- **Destructive Button**: Red background, white text
- **Success Button**: Green background, white text

#### Cards
- White background
- Light shadow (0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1))
- Rounded corners (12px)
- 24px padding

#### Navigation
- Sidebar with collapsible sections
- Top navigation with user profile, notifications, and search
- Breadcrumbs for deep navigation paths

#### Forms
- Floating labels that animate on focus
- Clear validation states with helpful error messages
- Toggle switches for boolean options
- Dropdown menus with search functionality

#### Modals
- Center screen with overlay background
- Prominent close button
- Action buttons aligned to the right

